            <description><![CDATA[【每天1斤白酒，肿瘤塞满脖子！67岁大叔半夜憋醒才发现不对劲<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】67岁的陈大叔，每天1斤白酒是常规操作，这一喝就是40年。不过几年前，陈大叔发现自己的身体不太对劲，肉眼可见脖子上出现了俩疙瘩。近几年双侧腋下竟鼓起两个大包，渐渐影响到了陈大叔的日常生活，甚至睡到半夜，会突然喘不过气，直接被憋醒，他这才开始慌，赶紧去医院做检查。检查结果一出，竟是良性对称性脂肪瘤！也叫<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%A9%AC%E5%BE%B7%E9%BE%99%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#马德龙病#</span></a>。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fh-Xk03Yi-SZKnEtyPJ4Tmg" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">指导专家：北京大学深圳医院乳甲外科副主任医师 李朋</span></a><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hajhdedp93j20v950cay6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hajhdfcx11j20v941anfj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hajhdfyo0mj20v966s1kx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
