            <description><![CDATA[【节后上班打不起精神咋办？4招帮你满血复活<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[春游家族]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/2021_YoungFamily_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】返工第一天，感觉身心俱疲？假期过后，如何调整身心状态，避免节后综合征？①恢复生活规律，睡前减少电子产品使用，保证睡眠，克服起床困难；②固定三餐时间，吃七分饱，避免肠胃紊乱；③多开窗通风，避免久坐，减少疲劳烦躁；④适当安排散步、慢跑、瑜伽等轻度运动。看👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4862635716575291" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1haij43zvbwj62xa1n8qv602.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/rlgkWXESlx082GA5niH601041200futT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675070545&amp;ssig=Z%2BtJYJySHu&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/d9rBrdvilx082GA59euQ010412007XHB0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675070545&amp;ssig=DQna44PLUc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/oCjwlcS1lx082GA545Fu0104120058300E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675070545&amp;ssig=GzQ4fdMMsp&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4862635716575291&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
